Posts.Content: are there other symptoms with breast cancer, without having any lumps?
Posts.Title: symptoms

Posts.Content: thank you both for your answers. i have not had a mamogram in 8 years. just always seem busy taking care of every one else. my left breast feels a little heavier than before and i have a nagging pain well not really pain but discomfort under my breast and just below my arm pit.i also worry, if not breast cancer than maybe lung cancer, i had smoked for 25 years and quit 13 years ago. thank you again for your input. kat
